articles.author: Jon Porter
articles.title: Disney delays Deadpool 3 and other Marvel films as actors' strike ends - The Verge
articles.description: Deadpool 3, Captain America: Brave New World, Blade, and Thunderbolts have all been given new release dates as the actors strike comes to an end.
